<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="approach-n">approach <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'prəʊtʃ/    美 /ə'prəʊtʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>靠近；接近：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the approach of autumn
秋天的来临</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The students stopped talking at the teacher's approach.
老师一走近，学生们就不说话了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>通道；道路</strong></h4>
<p>a road or path, etc. leading to sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All <strong>approaches to</strong> the town were blocked.
所有去城里的路都被堵住了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(处理...的) 方法；(达到...的) 途径</strong></h4>
<p>a way of dealing with sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She decided to <strong>adopt / take a</strong> different <strong>approach to</strong> the problem.
她决定采取不同的途径解决这个问题。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The job market has changed and our <strong>approach to</strong> finding work must change as well.
就业市场变了，我们找工作的方法也必须改变。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>At the meeting they discussed three different approaches <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the study of mathematics.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to  </p></div>